      "path": "infra/workshop-template.yaml",
      "staticContent": "CRITICAL - FILE TRUNCATION NOTICE\n\nThe file infra/workshop-template.yaml has been partially loaded - there are 1190 total lines in this file but only 850 lines were read.\n\nREQUIRED ACTIONS BEFORE PROCEEDING:\n1. VERIFY COMPLETENESS: Check if all relevant code (symbols/functions/classes) is visible in the current view\n2. IF INCOMPLETE:\n  - Use grepSearch to locate specific symbols\n  - Then use readFile with start_line/end_line parameters to view those sections\n  - Repeat readFile to read subsequent chunks 1000 lines at a time until the complete function or class definition is visible to you.\n  - Do not stop reading in the middle of a relevant comment block or code block or function definition or class definition\n  - Continue this process until you have gathered ALL relevant code\n\nHARD STOP - DO NOT PROCEED UNTIL:\n- You have confirmed you've seen all necessary code blocks to their completion\n- Or have used grepSearch/readFile to locate missing sections\n- You are 100% certain you have a complete view of all relevant code\n\nRemember: Partial code analysis can lead to incorrect conclusions. Just because you can see the symbol doesn't mean you have its full definition!\n\n   <file name=\"infra/workshop-template.yaml\" language=\"yaml\"  truncated=\"true\">\n   <content>\n   Resources:\n  RolesWorkshopRoleBD50F06E:\n    Type: AWS::IAM::Role\n    Properties:\n      AssumeRolePolicyDocument:\n        Statement:\n          - Action: sts:AssumeRole\n            Effect: Allow\n            Principal:\n              Service: ec2.amazonaws.com\n        Version: \"2012-10-17\"\n      ManagedPolicyArns:\n        - Fn::Join:\n            - \"\"\n            - - \"arn:\"\n              - Ref: AWS::Partition\n              - :iam::aws:policy/ReadOnlyAccess\n        - Fn::Join:\n            - \"\"\n            - - \"arn:\"\n              - Ref: AWS::Partition\n              - :iam::aws:policy/AmazonSSMManagedInstanceCore\n        - Fn::Join:\n            - \"\"\n            - - \"arn:\"\n              - Ref: AWS::Partition\n              - :iam::aws:policy/CloudWatchAgentServerPolicy\n        - Ref: RolesWorkshopIdeUserPolicy2666D138\n      RoleName: ide-user\n  RolesWorkshopRoleDefaultPolicy8F009E9D:\n    Type: AWS::IAM::Policy\n    Properties:\n      PolicyDocument:\n        Statement:\n          - Action:\n              - secretsmanager:DescribeSecret\n              - secretsmanager:GetSecretValue\n            Effect: Allow\n            Resource:\n              Ref: IdeIdePasswordSecretF3482811\n        Version: \"2012-10-17\"\n      PolicyName: RolesWorkshopRoleDefaultPolicy8F009E9D\n      Roles:\n        - Ref: RolesWorkshopRoleBD50F06E\n  RolesWorkshopIdeUserPolicy2666D138:\n    Type: AWS::IAM::ManagedPolicy\n    Properties:\n      Description: \"\"\n      Path: /\n      PolicyDocument:\n        Statement:\n          - Action: aws-marketplace:Subscribe\n            Condition:\n              \"Null\":\n                aws-marketplace:ProductId: \"false\"\n              ForAllValues:StringEquals:\n                aws-marketplace:ProductId:\n                  - prod-4pmewlybdftbs\n                  - prod-4dlfvry4v5hbi\n                  - prod-cx7ovbu5wex7g\n                  - prod-5oba7y7jpji56\n                  - b7568428-a1ab-46d8-bab3-37def50f6f6a\n                  - 38e55671-c3fe-4a44-9783-3584906e7cad\n            Effect: Allow\n            Resource: \"*\"\n          - Action:\n              - aws-marketplace:Unsubscribe\n              - aws-marketplace:ViewSubscriptions\n              - bedrock:*\n            Effect: Allow\n            Resource: \"*\"\n          - Action:\n              - cloudwatch:*\n              - codewhisperer:*\n              - ecr:*\n              - eks:*\n              - events:*\n              - iam:CreateOpenIDConnectProvider\n              - iam:TagOpenIDConnectProvider\n              - q:*\n              - secretsmanager:*\n              - ssm:*\n              - sts:*\n            Effect: Allow\n            Resource: \"*\"\n            Sid: AllowedServicesEKS\n          - Action: iam:PassRole\n            Effect: Allow\n            Resource:\n              - !Sub arn:aws:iam::${AWS::AccountId}:role/jvm-analysis-service*\n              - !Sub arn:aws:iam::${AWS::AccountId}:role/unicorn*\n            Sid: PassRoleEKS\n          - Action:\n              - iam:AttachRolePolicy\n              - iam:CreatePolicy\n              - iam:CreatePolicyVersion\n              - iam:CreateRole\n              - iam:DeletePolicy\n              - iam:DeletePolicyVersion\n              - iam:DeleteRole\n              - iam:DeleteRolePolicy\n              - iam:DetachRolePolicy\n              - iam:PassRole\n              - iam:PutRolePolicy\n              - iam:TagRole\n            Effect: Allow\n            Resource:\n              - !Sub arn:aws:iam::${AWS::AccountId}:policy/*AWSLambdaTracerAccessExecutionRole*\n              - !Sub arn:aws:iam::${AWS::AccountId}:policy/*Unicorn*\n              - !Sub arn:aws:iam::${AWS::AccountId}:policy/*unicorn*\n              - !Sub arn:aws:iam::${AWS::AccountId}:role/*Unicorn*\n              - !Sub arn:aws:iam::${AWS::AccountId}:role/*unicorn*\n              - !Sub arn:aws:iam::${AWS::AccountId}:role/jvm-analysis-service*\n            Sid: IamLimitedAccessForUnicorns\n          - Action:\n              - application-signals:*\n              - apprunner:*\n              - cloudformation:*\n              - codeartifact:*\n              - dynamodb:*\n              - ec2:*\n              - ecs:*\n              - elasticloadbalancing:*\n              - lambda:*\n              - logs:*\n              - s3:*\n              - tag:*\n              - xray:*\n            Effect: Allow\n            Resource: \"*\"\n            Sid: AllowedServicesOthers\n          - Action: ec2:RunInstances\n            Condition:\n              StringLike:\n                ec2:InstanceType:\n                  - \"*4xlarge\"\n        